snippet.title: Star Breaker: Today in Games (JP)
snippet.description:
Release Date: February 10, 1994 (Japan) - TurboGrafx CD 

Join me on a nostalgic journey through gaming history! In this series, I celebrate video game anniversaries by playing a different game on the exact day it was originally released. From retro classics to modern masterpieces, we'll discover a diverse range of titles and relive the magic of gaming's past. Let's take a trip down memory lane - one game, one anniversary, one day at a time. Please like and subscribe if you enjoy the content.
